article.contentHtml:
질문할 어플 (새카봇, 젤브봇, 메신저봇, 닼토봇, 기타)
=> 메신저봇

질문할 소스
=>
importPackage(org.apache.http);
importPackage(java.io);
importPackage(java.net);
importPackage(java.util);

const BasicNameValuePair = org.apache.http.message.BasicNameValuePair;
const URIBuilder = org.apache.http.client.utils.URIBuilder;
const KEY = "비밀";
const URL = "비밀";


function response(room,msg,sender,isGroupChat,replier){
var paratmers = new ArrayList();
paratmers.add(new BasicNameValuePair("start","1"));
paratmers.add(new BasicNameValuePair("limit","5000"));
paratmers.add(new BasicNameValuePair("convert","USD"));
try {
var result = makeAPICall(paratmers);
replier.reply(result);
} catch (e) {
replier.reply("Error: cannot access content - " + e.toString());
    }
}

makeAPICall = (parameters) =>{
    var response_content = "";
    var query = new org.apache.http.client.utils.URIBuilder();
    query.setScheme("https");
    query.setHost(URL);
    query.addParameters(parameters);

    var client = HttpClients.createDefault();
    var request = new HttpGet(query.build());
    request.setHeader(HttpHeaders.ACCEPT, "application/json");
    request.addHeader("X-CMC_PRO_API_KEY", KEY);
    var response = client.execute(request);
    try {
        replier.reply(response.getStatusLine());
        var entity = response.getEntity();
        response_content = EntityUtils.toString(entity);
        EntityUtils.consume(entity);
    } finally {
        response.close();
    }
    return response_content;
}

질문내용
=> 
Error: cannot access content - TypeError: [JavaPackage org.apache.http.client.utils.URIBuilder] is not a function, it is object. 라는 오류가 계속 발생...왜그럴까요 고인물님들?

var query = new org.apache.http.client.utils.URIBuilder();
query.setScheme("https");
query.setHost(URL);

이 부분 이애요.


(말머리 등록 하셨나요? Yes / No)
